subsection.text:
The Secretary of Education shall carry out a program under which the Secretary makes grants to
			 local educational agencies, to be used by the local educational agencies
			 for one or both of the following:

paragraph.text:
having jurisdiction over a geographic area with respect to which the Director of the Centers for
			 Disease Control and Prevention has determined that the prevalence of
			 asthma is at least 10 percent higher than the national average;
